'''Koodh''' ({{lang-en|Coat}}; {{lang-ar|معطف}}) waa shay dabacsan oo ka samaysan [[dun]], ama [[cudbi]], ama [[harag]] kaasi oo la tolay. Koodhku wuxuu ka mid yahay [[dhar|dharka dadka]] kaasi oo inta badan loo xidho si jidhka uga difaaco [[Qaboow|dhaxan]]ta. Dharka waxaa laga sameeyaa dun ka timaada haraga [[xoolo|xoolaha]], [[xayawaan]]ka iyo [[cudbi]]ga iyo noocyo aartifishal ah. Marka dharka la samaynayo waxa la isticmaalaa habab badan oo kala duwan, waxaa ugu caansan tolida, mareegida, iyo isku xidhxidhka dunta.<ref>Barber, Elizabeth Wayland (1994). ''Women's Work. The first 20,000 Years'', p.135.Norton & Company, New York. {{ISBN|0-393-31348-4}}</ref> 
==Hordhac==
Koodhku wuxuu ka mid yahay dharka joogtada ah ee rag iyo dumarba kaasi oo loo xidho in jidhka ka difaaco dhaxanta iyo qaboowga. Sidoo kale, koodhka waxaa loo xidhaa xarago iyo isqurxin, dunida maanta waxaa jira shaqooyinka qaar ay khasab tahay in shaqaaluhu ku soo labistaan koodh. Guud ahaan, koodhku waa maro la tolay taasi oo leh qaab le'eg qofka xidhanaya ama isticmaalaya sheygaasi. Shaadhku wuxuu leeyahay astaamo u gaar ah oo ka duwan noocyada kale ee dharka. Astaamaha ugu muhiimsan ee shaadhasha waxaa ka mid ah raqabada, jeeb iyo galuusyo (badhano) badan oo laabta ku dhex yaala.<ref>William L. Brown III, "Some Thoughts on Men's Shirts in America, 1750-1900", Thomas Publications, Gettysburg, PA 1999. {{ISBN|1-57747-048-6}}, p. 7</ref> 
==Magaca==
Ereyga '''''Koodh''''' asal ahaan waa mid [[Af-Ingiriis]] ah oo waxaan ka soo xiganahay luuqadaasi Ingiriiska ereyga ''Coat''.<ref>Dorothy K. Burnham, "Cut My Cote", Royal Ontario Museum, Toronto, Ontario 1973. {{ISBN|0-88854-046-9}}, p. 14</ref> 
==Dharka==
'''[[Dhar]]ka''' ({{lang-en|Textile ama Cloth}}; {{lang-ar|نسيج (قماش)}}) waa shay dabacsan oo ka samaysan [[dun]] la xardhay. Dharka waxaa laga sameeyaa dun ka timaada haraga [[xoolo|xoolaha]], [[xayawaan]]ka iyo [[cudbi]]ga iyo noocyo aartifishal ah.<ref>C. Willett and Phillis Cunnington, ''The History of Underclothes'', Dover Publications Inc., New York 1992. {{ISBN|0-486-27124-2}} pp. 23–25</ref> Marka dharka la samaynayo waxa la isticmaalaa habab badan oo kala duwan, waxaa ugu caansan tolida, mareegida, iyo isku xidhxidhka dunta. God ku yaala galbeedka wadanka Joorjiya ee bariga [[Yurub]] ayaa waxa laga helay qidcad harag oo lagu wado in dhar ahaan loo isticmaali jirey wakhti hada laga joogo 34,000 oo sano. Dharka guud ahaan waxaa la isku yidhaahdaa '''Hu<nowiki>'</nowiki>'''; kaasi oo u kala baxa noocyo badan. Kugu ugu muhiimsan ee dadku isticmaalaan maalin kasta waxaa ka mid ah: [[surwaal]]ka, [[shaadh]]ka, [[dirac]]a, [[shalmad]]a, [[goono (dhar)|goonada]], [[koodh (dhar)|koodhka]], [[kabbo|kabaha]] iyo kuwo kale oo badan.<ref>''"[[surwaal]]ka, [[shaadh]]ka, [[dirac]]a, [[shalmad]]a, [[goono (dhar)|goonada]], [[koodh (dhar)|koodhka]], [[kabbo|kabaha]]"''</ref><ref>C. Willett and Phillis Cunnington, ''The History of Underclothes'', Dover Publications Inc., New York 1992. {{ISBN|0-486-27124-2}} pp. 54</ref>
